Yes that’s what I made a week 💰💳 ! 

Here’s some tricks which I apply in my content creation journey & you should apply too 🫶🏻

• I earn/charge every figure according to the deliverables the  brand wants . 
• I don’t let any opportunity to go away & grab that as soon as possible, so that my opportunity doesn’t becomes somebody else’s opportunity. It’s said if you don’t , any other will . 
• I make strategies & ask the brands to pay as soon as video goes live . 
• Am I charging less ? Yes I believe, but I also believe that little foot steps takes you to the big miles . 

If you believe in this post , do save for later 📪
